The '''Galtea Run''' was a hyperspace route located in the [[Kathol sector/Legends|Kathol sector]] in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]] of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. The Galtea Run, along with the [[Sebiris Run]], crossed the [[Marcol Void/Legends|Marcol Void]] into the [[Kathol Outback/Legends|Kathol Outback]]. The Galtea Run connected [[Galtea/Legends|Galtea]] to [[Timbra Ott]]. The hyperlane was also responsible for connecting the [[Kathol Outback/Legends|Kathol Outback]] with the majority of the Kathol sector, passing through such worlds as [[Binaros]], [[Jangelle]], [[Pitann]], [[Uukaablis]], and [[Exocron]].<ref name="KO">''[[The Kathol Outback]]''</ref>

